casebody.data:
No. 592. Max Alexander, Petitioner, v. Mills B. Lane et al. February 24, 1908. Mr. William Garrard, Mr. P. W. Meldrim and Mr. Garrard Glenn for petitioner. Mr. Robert M. Hitch for respondents.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
